martial_arts.title: Martial Arts
martial_arts.description: Immerse yourself in a disciplined artistry, be entertained by fantastic gravity-defying feats, and finally understand those Wu-Tang references.

11420.title: Return of The Street Fighter
11420.description: Sonny Chiba is back! This time, he is hired by the mob to execute a respected karate master by ripping out his vocal cords. When he later refuses, Tsurugi is put on the death list himself.

11427.title: The Street Fighter's Last Revenge
11427.description: No one can stop Tsurugi's fists of fury after mobsters double-crossed him and murder his girlfriend!

257162.title: Battle Creek Brawl
257162.description: The life of a Chinese man seeking fame in 1930’s Chicago is turned upside-down when the head of a mob syndicate takes his brother's fiance hostage.

257167.title: City Hunter
257167.description: P.I. Ryu Saeba’s first impulse is to turn down a job to find the beautiful runaway daughter of a publishing tycoon—until he sees a picture of her.

257298.title: The Protector
257298.description: A pair of New York City detectives are sent to Hong Kong to go on the hunt for a drug lord who has kidnapped the daughter of a former associate.

272763.title: Crime Story
272763.description: Inspector Eddie Chan fights mobsters, corruption, and his own personal demons as he searches for a kidnapped business man in Hong Kong and Taiwan.

279388.title: Bushido Man
279388.description: Toramaru, lord of integrated martial arts Mugen-ga-ryu, ends his training journey and visits his master, Gensai.

282523.title: Goodbye Bruce Lee: His Last Game of Death
282523.description: A kung fu expert is approached by the director of the late Bruce Lee's unfinished film and asked to help in bringing the film to the silver screen.

284003.title: Street Fighter Alpha
284003.description: Brought together by the mysterious death of their martial arts master, Ken and Ryu must overcome a momentous challenge unlike any other.

302433.title: Kickboxer 2
302433.description: Fighter Tong Po will stop at nothing to challenge one retired kickboxer, who must recover to face the man who injured him and killed his brothers.

303002.title: American Ninja 4
303002.description: Two martial arts fighters are sent to stop a terrorist and a group of ninjas from blowing up New York City in this action thriller.

304780.title: Kickboxer 3
304780.description: David Sloan travels to Rio de Janeiro and puts his life on the line as he confronts a gang of terrorists in order to free a kidnapped girl.

307753.title: Kickboxer
307753.description: After a kickboxing champ is paralyzed fighting Thailand’s top fighter, his brother vows vengeance but must learn Muay Thai to fight back.

376059.title: Covert Operation
376059.description: When a rescue mission for a British operative in North Korea goes wrong, Gabriel must take on an entire military installation to bring everyone home.

376068.title: Muay Thai Fighter
376068.description: When a childhood boxing club falls apart, three friends start down a dangerous path when they begin fighting underground for money.

376464.title: Lawless Kingdom
376464.description: Four detectives with superhuman abilities must solve a series of murders after discovering clues to an unsolved case. But can they survive?

417610.title: White Tiger
417610.description: After a Chinese drug lord murders his partner, a tough DEA agent teams up with a mysterious beauty and makes an uneasy alliance to exact revenge.

456906.title: Ninja
456906.description: A ninja-in-training returns to New York to protect a legendary chest of weapons from high-flying assassins that test his skills at every turn.

460882.title: Bko Bangkok Knockout
460882.description: A range of martial art disciplines are unleashed as  a group of fight club friends join forces and fight for their lives to rescue a kidnapped friend.

472651.title: Force Four
472651.description: Four black belt fighters deliver their own form of butt-kicking justice after a priceless African statue is stolen and its messenger is murdered.

483940.title: The Prisoner
483940.description: A cop goes undercover to infiltrate a deadly prison where a team of mercernaries is being assembled.

490122.title: Sakura Killer
490122.description: After ninja thieves steal a secret gene-splicing formula, a U.S. colonel sends two of his men to Taiwan to keep the ninjas from selling it to Russia.

496010.title: Martial Law II: Undercover
496010.description: As two undercover cops/martial arts masters investigate the death of a fellow cop, the tangled web of crime and seduction only gets more complicated.

496262.title: Martial Law
496262.description: An undercover cop trained in martial arts tries to rescue his criminal brother from the grip of a gang led by a kung fu expert.

497116.title: Legend of the Red Dragon
497116.description: It takes a father and son team to battle the forces of evil throughout China, fighting with honor to defend the weak through fast-motion kung fu.

497642.title: Fist of Fury
497642.description: Bruce Lee stars in this iconic action film about a student who fights for the honor of the oppressed Chinese people and to avenge his master’s murder

499293.title: Ong Bak 3: The Final Battle
499293.description: Picking up where the saga left off, Tien, who was captured and beaten, returns to the Kana Khone village, to learn new skills and face a final duel.

500676.title: Blood Money
500676.description: Martial arts star Zheng Liu shines in this fast-paced thriller involving a kidnapping, the Colombian drug cartel, and the Hong Kong Triad.

501418.title: Ninja: Shadow of a Tear
501418.description: When the life of a martial arts master is shattered by his wife’s brutal murder, he enlists an old friend to sharpen his skills and seek revenge.

505025.title: Kung Fu Killer
505025.description: After a martial arts instructor kills a man by mistake, he is imprisoned, until the police need his help taking down a vengeful killer.

506494.title: Kung Fu Yoga
506494.description: Two professors team up to locate a lost treasure and embark on an adventure that takes them from a Tibetan ice cave to a mountain temple in India.

516851.title: Shaolin vs Lama
516851.description: A kung-fu master searching for a true fighting rival goes up against a thieving monk who stole a scroll of every known fighting style in existence.

516855.title: Shaolin Invincible Guys
516855.description: An eagle claw fighter and a fighting con-man team up against underlords holding the con-man’s girlfriend hostage in a brothel as a prostitute.

516856.title: Shaolin Drunk Fighter
516856.description: The murder of a young man’s family by a group of ruthless martial art masters becomes his obsession in seeking ultimate revenge on them all.

518143.title: Two Heroes Shooting Stars
518143.description: Spectacular fighting styles are on display when a master of a Wing Chung style and a student of the Buddha's Palm join forces.

518146.title: The Shaolin Drunk Monkey
518146.description: A conceited martial arts master is challenged to a deadly duel by an opponent he assumes is less than worthy.

518148.title: Fury in Shaolin Temple
518148.description: When a young boy finds himself alone in the world after his adoptive father disappears following a fight, his first thought is to go to Shaolin.

520095.title: Cantonen Iron Kung Fu
520095.description: When Black Eagle, a wicked and greedy businessman, attempts to dominate the local supply routes, a brave laborer named Leung must fight him.

520214.title: Kung Fu Killer (English Dubbed)
520214.description: A wrongly imprisoned kung fu master is offered his freedom in exchange for helping the police catch a serial killer targeting martial arts experts.

521033.title: Dragon
521033.description: The quiet life of a village craftsman, who makes paper, is irrevocably shattered by the arrival of two notorious gangsters in the local general store.

522187.title: Blind Fist of Bruce
522187.description: A well-to-do villager learning kung-fu to protect himself and his family from gangsters encounters a conman mentor.

529519.title: Seven Swords: Bone of the Godmaker
529519.description: A fiendish cult seeking to release a demonic spirit from the underworld must first wrestle seven magic swords of the realm from four holy spirits.

541309.title: 2099: The Soldier Protocol
541309.description: A biotech experiment conducted by the military inside a prison gives an inmate with paralysis the ability to walk again, but at a torturous price.

543991.title: Circle of Iron
543991.description: The cult martial arts epic, based on Bruce Lee’s passion project, about a man who must fight a string of opponents for a mystical book of knowledge.

551192.title: Story of Drunken Master
551192.description: Beggar So’s attempts to train brother and sister team Chung and Gam Fa are interrupted when an enemy from Beggar So’s past arrives.

551209.title: He Has Nothing but Kung Fu
551209.description: After losing his memory and being left for dead, a fighter teams up with a beggar to take on the local triad gang.

551245.title: Of Cooks and Kung Fu
551245.description: A promising and disciplined young pupil learns an unorthodox style of martial arts from a wise mentor in order to stand up to an evil adversary.

551248.title: Bruce Le's Greatest Revenge (Way of the Dragon 2)
551248.description: A disciplined martial artist is tested when he is forced to defend his own honor after trying to keep the peace between rival groups.

551250.title: Born Invincible
551250.description: A group of martial arts students lead a quest for revenge against two formidable warlords who attacked and killed an innocent man.

551254.title: Seven Commandments of Kung Fu
551254.description: A notorious assassin and martial artist finds himself a young protégé in order to continue on with his wicked business of killing and mayhem.

551258.title: 36 Deadly Styles
551258.description: Get ready for martial-arts excellence and powerhouse fights as a young man learns the 8 Gods Fist technique to punish his father’s killers.

551289.title: Kung Fu Zombie
551289.description: A man faces a terrifying fight for life after his father enrages a psychotic exorcist who unleashes an insane zombie army against their family.

551298.title: The Big Showdown (Kung Fu Massacre)
551298.description: An exchange student’s homecoming is torn when he finds his family killed and his sister missing, leading him to team with a master kicker for revenge.

551301.title: Ninja Wolves
551301.description: An evil and envious eunuch betrays his Emperor with the two henchmen he was given as gifts, but his schemes and bloodshed soon take a deadly twist.

551320.title: Shaolin Brothers
551320.description: The supernatural and the martial arts combine as 3 undercover monk brothers fight against tyrannical government rulers shielded by deadly magic armor.

552523.title: Deadly Strike (Wanted! Bruce Li, Dead or Alive)
552523.description: A new police chief in a small town joins forces with prisoners and his deputies to bring a dangerous gang to justice.

555853.title: The Master
555853.description: A martial arts master's mother and students are seized after refusing to join the prince's army. To save them, he has only one path: all-out war.

560468.title: Railroad Tigers (Dubbed)
560468.description: A railroad worker in war-torn 1941 China leads a team of freedom fighters against the occupying Japanese army, in order to get food for the poor

560519.title: Rivals of the Silver Fox
560519.description: A young fighter trains with the legendary Silver Fox to successfully pass through the five deadly gates and defeat the notorious Devil Lodge gang.

560524.title: Warriors of Kung Fu
560524.description: After they were viciously attacked by a ruthless gang, two brothers must learn how to fight the criminals that took so much away from them.

560676.title: Police Story: Lockdown (Dubbed)
560676.description: While visiting his estranged daughter at a nightclub, a cop must spring into action, as an elaborate kidnapping plot unfolds right before his eyes.

560757.title: Tai Chi Zero (Dubbed)
560757.description: Traditional villagers are torn between a traveler, who teaches a powerful new form of Tai Chi, and a man who plans to build a railroad on their land.

560873.title: Ip Man: The Final Fight (Dubbed)
560873.description: In postwar Hong Kong, a real-life Wing Chun grandmaster rises to action once more, as kung fu rivals draw him into a dark, dangerous underworld.

561343.title: Hero of the Time
561343.description: A gang leader’s reign of terror over a small town is threatened by a government agent, so he unleashes a master of kung fu to knock out the avengers.

561518.title: Adventure at Shaolin
561518.description: Martial arts dazzler about the founder of Tai Chi and his quest to become an expert fighter as he learns two timeless techniques of self-defense.

561519.title: Chinese Super Ninjas 2 (Lady Ninja)
561519.description: A martial arts warrior learns that her brother fights for the opposite cause. Soon she pulls together a team of women warriors to stop her brother.

561525.title: Shaolin Drunken Monk (The 36th Chamber: The Final Encounter)
561525.description: After his temple is destroyed, a Shaolin disciple and a wandering beggar team up to take down the villain responsible in a duel of fighting styles.

565416.title: Damage
565416.description: Ex-con John Brickner joins an underground fighting community to pay for the heart transplant of the daughter of the man he killed.

569661.title: Fist 2 Fist: Weapon of Choice
569661.description: An ex-assassin who became a civilian to raise his brother’s orphaned daughter revives his skills when a San Francisco kingpin steals her for revenge.

569713.title: Fight Ring
569713.description: A martial artist struggling to make ends meet gets a chance at an underground fighting match where contestants fight in a ruthless battle-zone.

572756.title: Iceman (English Dub)
572756.description: Four hundred years after being frozen, a Ming Dynasty palace guard and his associates are thawed in modern day to resume the battle they left behind.

574758.title: Tiger Over Wall
574758.description: Based on real life events in 1919 Shanghai, a British diplomat’s missing dog leads a corrupt police captain to viciously ruin an innocent man’s life.

574796.title: Seven Steps of Kung Fu
574796.description: When a sleepy Chinese village is threatened by a dangerous gang, a kung fu master trains his young pupil to start picking off its members, one-by-one.

585836.title: The Pirates
585836.description: As a new dynasty prepares for power, a whale swallows the Emperor’s Royal Seal, bringing together misfits on the seas in search of the bounty reward.

588473.title: The Protector 2 (Dubbed)
588473.description: When a man is blamed for a crime boss’s death, he has to go on the run while evading the police, the man’s evil twin nieces, and a new crime lord.

588486.title: Merantau Dubbed
588486.description: A young man in rural West Indonesia has his life changed when he accepts merantau, a traditional rite of passage where men must leave the family home.

588490.title: Chocolate (Dubbed)
588490.description: A girl with only TV shows as a fight trainer becomes a violent thief to pay for her sick mom’s medical bills before she meets her Yakuza mob father.

589702.title: Kill Zone 2 (English Dub)
589702.description: After a Hong Kong police officer is sent to a Thai prison, he must stop the warden and a criminal from completing their organ harvesting plans.

589839.title: The Divine Fury
589839.description: A boy rejects Christianity when his father dies. As an adult prize fighter, he is a top success until a demonic wound appears in the palm of his hand.

590211.title: The Knight of Shadows (English Dub)
590211.description: A demon hunter is enlisted by a village to save the lives of young girls who have been kidnapped by dark forces that feed on their souls.

591361.title: Legend of the Tsunami Warrior (Dubbed)
591361.description: An action-packed tale of a brewing, epic war between a port city ruled by a Princess and a brutal pirate brigade led by a Prince and a sorcerer.

591376.title: Rise of the Legend (Dubbed)
591376.description: An extraordinarily powerful martial artist returns to where his father was assassinated to free the people from his nemesis, a ruthless crime lord.

592891.title: Sworn to Justice
592891.description: After attackers kill her sister and nephew, a psychologist, who possesses the gift of ESP, becomes a defense witness by day and an avenger by night.

592893.title: Red Sun Rising
592893.description: A Japanese detective teams up with an LA cop to track down the Yakuza assassin who killed his partner and shut down a weapons-smuggling operation.

593871.title: Razor Sharpe
593871.description: An actor looking for his big break gets the part of a martial-arts star in a movie but finds out that the murder and crime action is actually real.

599975.title: Attrition
599975.description: Axe is the leader of a special unit. He decides to retreat to the jungles of Asia, where he tries to reconcile with the life he has lived. When a desperate father asks him to save his kidnapped daughter, Axe must step in again.

602160.title: The 8 Masters
602160.description: After growing up in the Shaolin Temple, a budding martial artist studies the importance of patience and mercy and takes on the Eight Masters.

602186.title: Swift Shaolin Boxer
602186.description: A pair of warriors take on a band of ruthless criminals, fearlessly conquering a fortress and bringing down anyone who dares to stop them.

602187.title: Six Directions Boxing
602187.description: After the captain of the police looks into a warlord’s weapon trafficking history, he realizes it’s going to take more than guns to bring justice.

602188.title: Thundering Mantis
602188.description: A martial arts fan is always joking and getting into trouble with kung-fu routines, and he’ll need them after he enrages an infamous crime syndicate.

603619.title: Fatal Needles, Fatal Fist
603619.description: Meng Hu and Capt. Chow are super cops who are cracking down on crime with a vengeance, until several fighters get the drop on Chow, and ends up dead. Meng blames himself and retires from crime fighting to become a pathetic drunk, drowning in shame.

604310.title: Robin-B-Hood
604310.description: Thongs and Octopus grow attached to the baby they kidnapped for their landlord, which leads to complications in handing the him over.

604316.title: Seven Swords
604316.description: Seven exceptional warriors band together to protect a village from bounty hunters.

610943.title: The Dragon the Young Master
610943.description: A young man, an informant against local corruption in 1920s China, readies for a vicious martial-arts battle to avenge those who killed his father.

611159.title: Furious Avenger
611159.description: A man, who sees his family members slain and is captured during a war of resistance against invading foreign powers, sets out on a path of vengeance.

611331.title: Un Tipo Duro (Doblado)
611331.description: Un detective hace alarde de su estilo monkey kung al investigar el asesinato de la mujer del emperador con la ayuda de tres audaces guerreras.

611336.title: Los Invencibles Del Karate (Doblado)
611336.description: Tres discípulos del templo Shaolín se organizan para expulsar a quienes irrumpieron la paz de la población imponiendo impuestos y perpetuando abusos.

615155.title: Fist of the Red Dragon
615155.description: Manipulated by an evil imperial prince, opium-addicted young Beggar Su sets out to assassinate a righteous general until his wits catch up with him.

619654.title: Ip Man (English Dub)
619654.description: Tells the story of the brutality of the 1939 Japanese occupation of China through the eyes of the Wing Chun grandmaster who rose to fight against it.

619656.title: Ip Man 2 (English Dub)
619656.description: When the Wing Chun grandmaster moves to Hong Kong to open a school for the next generation of fighters, he’s forced to take on a corrupt cabal.

619660.title: Ip Man 3 (English Dub)
619660.description: Hong Kong, 1959. A crooked real estate developer leads a band of gangsters in a property coup that can only be stopped by the Wing Chun grandmaster.

619662.title: Kickboxer: Retaliation
619662.description: Following a Las Vegas match, an MMA champ is abducted and sent to a Bangkok prison where he must fight for his freedom against a 400-pound killer.

619837.title: Haphazard
619837.description: After a U.S. defense satellite containing missile activation codes crashes on an island off the coast of Thailand, three individuals race to find it.

622260.title: Sleeping Fist
622260.description: After a cop is beaten by a gang of thugs, he trains in the art of Sleeping Fist and, together with a cub and his master, seeks out his revenge.

623238.title: The Protector
623238.description: When his family’s elephants are stolen from the Bangkok jungle, a young fighter travels to Australia to retrieve them from the dangerous Thai mafia.

626674.title: Chinese Hercules
626674.description: A muscular martial arts warrior tries to leave his past behind and becomes a dock worker, but the cruel owner’s iron fist leads him to fight again.

626678.title: Dragon Fist
626678.description: This vintage Jackie Chan film from 1979 sees him as a worker who becomes involved in a hardcore feud between his dead boss’s killer and gangsters.

626742.title: Master of the Flying Guillotine
626742.description: An evil and bling Kung Fu master travels to a martial arts competition with his secret weapon that can decapitate any one-armed foe he sees.

626765.title: American Fighter
626765.description: A young wrestler is forced to get gritty and stay strong when he enters an underground fighting ring to pay for his mother’s medical treatments.

626784.title: Revenge Of The Shaolin Master
626784.description: Legendary director and fight choreographer of “The Matrix” films does double duty on this tale of revenge, corruption, and epic fight sequences.

626972.title: Death Duel of Kung Fu
626972.description: Two great fighters clash in an epic battle of supremacy as Ching Ming prepares for all-out war between his fighters and Taiwan’s kung fu artists.

626979.title: Dance of the Drunken Mantis
626979.description: A young martial arts master must face off against a fierce rival named Rubber Legs who has blended two deadly fighting styles for ultimate domination.

627610.title: Fearless Hyena
627610.description: Jackie Chan stars in this classic as a young country man taught a secret form of Kung Fu by his grandfather who can’t keep his skills to himself.

627736.title: Snake the Tiger the Crane
627736.description: An Emperor’s daughter and a fierce warrior with one arm team together to defeat the latest invaders coming to destroy their kingdom.

627763.title: Ninja Death 1
627763.description: A late-‘80s martial arts film about the owner of a prostitution brothel who is also a secret kung fu artist on the side with a powerful “Master.”

629847.title: Sharp Fists in Kung Fu
629847.description: A kind rich man’s nasty son comes home with an equally malicious woman. As they wreak havoc, the Kung Fu kid shows up to put them both in check.

629850.title: Fearless Kung Fu Elements
629850.description: A family in China being plagued by a demonic entity use the five elements in the universe – gold, wood, earth, water and fire – in a kung fu battle.

629853.title: Lady Iron Monkey
629853.description: A young woman raised by apes, who is an expert kung fu fighter, is deceived by the false romantic attraction of a prince who uses her for her powers.

629854.title: Shaolin Master and the Kid
629854.description: The work of a federal officer in Hong Kong becomes personal when he’s assigned to take down every one of his late brother’s evil assassins.

629855.title: Snake Deadly Act
629855.description: A smug rich kid who makes it his entertainment to start brawls all over gets saved by the Snake Fist Master after he almost gets killed for fighting.

631172.title: Prophet
631172.description: Don “The Dragon” Wilson leads with his signature action moves as a CIA agent whose terrorist targets keep getting murdered before he can arrest them.

632203.title: The Sanctuary (English)
632203.description: A fast-paced action tale about a Muay Thai warrior and an archaeology student battling against evil criminals who stole Thailand’s national treasure.

637768.title: Dragon's Snake Fist
637768.description: Some of the best choreographed fight scenes ever filmed highlight this saga of two rival martial arts schools’ deadly rivalry across many generations.

637899.title: Apokalips X (Dubbed)
637899.description: In the wake of a global nuclear holocaust, survivors in 2047 have gathered into clans prepared to battle to the death to rule what’s left of humanity.

639597.title: Shogun's Ninja
639597.description: A 16th century warlord sends a battle commander on a decades-long quest to find two daggers that are the key to a treasure of gold that ensures power.

639644.title: Twin Dragons
639644.description: The lives of identical twin brothers separated at birth comically converge when the symphony conductor and cunning mechanic cross paths as adults.

645514.title: Bruce Lee the Invincible
645514.description: Incredible fight sequences define this tale of a kung-fu killer who can only be stopped by a fighter who knows Bruce Lee’s deft and sharp style

645969.title: Sword of Desperation
645969.description: An expert swordsman is on a path of palace intrigue, redemption, and death when he is rehired after openly killing his master’s favorite mistress.

646730.title: Fists of Fury
646730.description: A kung-fu fighter discovers the ice factory where he works is a front for the same drug trafficking ring responsible for the deaths of his relatives.

649977.title: Master Z: Ip Man Legacy (English Dub)
649977.description: Dave Bautista and Michelle Yeoh throw fists in this story of a defeated criminal who gets drawn closer into a life of crime when he becomes a waiter.

649979.title: Shadow (English Dub)
649979.description: The multiple-award-winning action film about a kingdom commander facing betrayal at all angles who has a lookalike shadow who can slay his foes.

652107.title: Kung Fu Killer (Español)
652107.description: Un monje de raza blanca con sed de justicia se infiltra en el bajo mundo de Shanghai para eliminar a los asesinos de su gran maestro espiritual.

654072.title: The Warrior's Way
654072.description: The world's finest warrior-assassin leaves Japan to find an old friend in the American Badlands rather than kill the infant queen of a rival clan.

655961.title: Duel of Flying Kicks
655961.description: A corrupt mayor tries to overtake his town by cutting off supply routes, but two kung fu mercenaries are about to make sure that doesn't happen.

659219.title: Kung Fu Hero Wang Yu
659219.description: Set in the late Qing Dynasty, follow the extraordinary story of the adventures of legendary swordsman Wang Wu, said to be based on true facts.

659271.title: Gambling for Head
659271.description: A kung fu master, whose brother was murdered by gangsters over an unpaid gambling debt, sets out with a vengeance, unleashing his martial arts skills.

659531.title: Martial Arts History Museum Biography: Don Wilson
659531.description: The museum honors Don “the dragon” Wilson, an 11-time World Kickboxing Champion in three weight classes who scored 47 knockouts over four decades.

659533.title: Martial Arts History Museum Biography: Cynthia Rothrock
659533.description: The museum honors one of the most iconic figures in martial arts history: lionheart warrior Cynthia Rothrock, known as the “Queen of Martial Arts.”

664251.title: Lord of the Streets
664251.description: When a trainer refuses to make his fighter throw a match, a notorious gangster collects the debt by killing his fighter and kidnapping his daughter.

666134.title: Detective Dee Tongtian Hierarch
666134.description: The Tang Dynasty emperor engages a famous detective, when he hears a political rumor about a plot to stage a coup and replace the sitting empress.

666141.title: Drunken Master Su Qier
666141.description: When a young martial artist is framed for drug possession, and his family is destroyed, he learns new skills from a master who helps him seek revenge.

666286.title: The Art of War by Sun Tzu (Challenge of the Invincibles)
666286.description: Charts the exploits of the famed scholar, hero and master strategist as he uses his art of war in the martial arts world to devastating effect.

666938.title: Mysterious Heroes (Wu Tang Swordsman)
666938.description: The enemies of the late Lau Tien, master of the deadly 13-sword style, vow to destroy his successor.

671826.title: Lady Bloodfight
671826.description: Upon arriving in Hong Kong, an American woman is beaten up and mugged by thugs. She's taken in by a martial arts master who trains her into a fighter.

673876.title: The Deadly Duo
673876.description: A group of fighters accompanied by a mysterious stranger set out to free a kidnapped Sung Dynasty prince being held in a fortress by elite fighters.

673900.title: Shaolin Death Squad
673900.description: A group of brave monk warriors fight to the death to keep their Shaolin temple from being overthrown by the evil Qing Dynasty emperor Yung Cheng.

673908.title: Triple Impact
673908.description: Three experts in combat venture into the jungles of Asia to find and retrieve a priceless artifact before a group of mercenaries finds it first.

675653.title: Snuff Bottle Connection
675653.description: A conspiracy by Chinese traitors is uncovered by an agent. After an investigator is killed, Shao Ting Shang must figure out who is behind the murder.

675829.title: Top Fighter
675829.description: Filmmaker Toby Russell explores the history of martial arts in cinema and the styles of iconic actors like Bruce Lee, Jackie Chan, and Jet Li.

680202.title: Kung Fu Master (Sub Esp)
680202.description: In this action-packed martial arts film, a Shaolin monk faces deadly obstacles in his quest to destroy a violent alliance that threatens his people.

681768.title: Kickboxer: Vengeance
681768.description: When a brutal fighter kills his brother, Kurt travels to Thailand to train with a legendary martial arts master and avenge his death.

682112.title: Kung Fu Killer II
682112.description: To avenge the murder of his Wudang Grandmaster, White Crane, a monk and spiritual master of the martial arts, infiltrates the Shanghai underground.

685722.title: An Eye for an Eye
685722.description: An SFPD undercover narcotics cop sets out to avenge his partner's death and destroy a drug smuggling ring operated by the Chinese Triads.

686064.title: Sun Dragon
686064.description: When a Black Panther's family is wiped out by a ruthless band of assassins, he sets out to avenge their murder with the help of a martial arts master.

689752.title: Drunken Master
689752.description: After a series of incidents, a mischievous yet righteous young man is sent into a brutal training program run by a master of drunken martial arts.

691076.title: Armour of God
691076.description: Asian Hawk and his bumbling sidekick are sent on a quest through Europe to find a mysterious treasure held by a shadowy organization of monks.

691397.title: El Retorno Del Tigre (Doblado)
691397.description: Chang Wong, astuto y suave, y su imponente compañera idean un elaborado plan para acabar con una red de tráfico de heroína dirigida por nefasto Paul.

691414.title: Godfathers of Fury
691414.description: Based on the Small Swords Society of the Taiping Rebellion, a stranger in a black fedora must clear his name in the murder of Shanghai’s godfather.

694888.title: Iron Protector
694888.description: A martial arts master and successor of an ancient Chinese clan must unleash his secret fighting techniques as the bodyguard of a spoiled rich girl.

697146.title: The Golden Cane Warrior
697146.description: After their master is killed, a pair of student fighters mount a personal campaign to find the Golden Cane relic before it falls into the wrong hands.

697872.title: The Martial Arts Kid
697872.description: A troubled teen from Cleveland faces bullies in his new Cocoa Beach, Florida digs and learns martial arts to gain confidence and self defense skills.

702703.title: Triple Threat
702703.description: When a hit gets taken out on a billionaire's daughter by a major crime syndicate, it’s mercenaries versus assassins in an all-out war.

703176.title: Money Fight
703176.description: Based on true events, this full-contact action drama, loaded with authentic mixed martial arts, is a transcending inspirational story of redemption.

703617.title: Kung Fu-Ry
703617.description: A martial arts master who moonlights as a professional hitman finds himself in the middle of a battle between his mob syndicate and law enforcement.

711172.title: Toque De Muerte (Sub Esp)
711172.description: Un reportero entrevista a luchadores y promotores sobre Bruce Lee, entremezclado con imágenes de películas antiguas y material de pseudo-documental.

711903.title: Killing Crisis
711903.description: Falsely accused of the murder of a corrupt late-Jiajing period Ming Dynasty official, Li Xin escapes from prison to find the truth and save lives.

711907.title: Damocles
711907.description: A man finds himself in the center of a far-reaching conspiracy after being told he’s the legacy of a millenniums-old secret assassin organization.

713114.title: Kung Fu League
713114.description: Fei Ying Xiong summons the best kung fu masters in history to learn the highest level of martial arts and help him defeat all who stand in his way.

713123.title: The Bloody Blade of King Lanling
713123.description: The legendary story of Gao Changgong, the high-ranking general of the Northern Qi dynasty, who must defend the throne from magic arts after the war.

713155.title: Fang Shiyu: The Winner Is King
713155.description: With help from his companion, a wrongly imprisoned legendary kung fu fighter must recover treasure for his master and eliminate a corrupt official.

713532.title: New Fong Sai Yuk: Battle in Cliff City
713532.description: To improve the miserable lives of a lawless city’s residents, Fang Shiyu decides to take down its ruthless local gang leader, Zhang Jinhong.

713897.title: Invincible Kung Fu Trio
713897.description: During the Qing dynasty, a pair of hapless kung fu fans learn the art of Goose Wing and Mighty Kicks from an old beggar man to fight against Bolo.

713898.title: Bruce Kung Fu Girls
713898.description: Five young women staying with their police superintendent uncle in Hong Kong put their kung fu skills into practice against a gang of thieves.

713899.title: Stranger From Canton
713899.description: As Qing Dynasty officials hunt down and brutally execute loyalists to Sun, a young woman goes undercover on a train to assist a guerrilla group.

715441.title: Sho Kosugi Ninja Theatre Vol. 6: Ninja Phantom Heroes
715441.description: A ninja prisoner at a hard labor camp is released when he agrees to accept a mission to take down a criminal organization.

715586.title: Shaolin Dolemite
715586.description: Rudy Ray Moore's iconic Dolemite character returns, this time traveling to Shaolin, in this film Moore created by re-dubbing a 1986 kung fu movie.

715593.title: The Kid From Tibet
715593.description: A Tibetan monk is sent to Hong Kong to recover a coveted magical bottle, which is said to protect the region from invasion by the evil Black Section.

716485.title: Thunderbolt
716485.description: An expert mechanic tasked with capturing the ringleader of a street-racing gang finds himself fighting for his family’s life in a race to the death.

718343.title: Karate Girl: Kick to the Groin
718343.description: A teenager and secret karate master must battle the gang that killed her parents to free her kidnapped sister and protect her family’s trophy belt.

718537.title: The Paper Tigers
718537.description: Three kung fu prodigies-turned-washed-up, middle-aged men must juggle their dead-end jobs, dad duties and old grudges to avenge their master’s murder.

724151.title: Rage of Honor
724151.description: When his partner is murdered by drug dealers, a narcotics cop vows revenge and, disobeying orders, tracks the killers from Singapore to Buenos Aires.

725754.title: Los Bastones Invencibles De Shaolin (Doblado)
725754.description: El Luchador del Asta que Parte el Aire, se opone a su búsqueda del control del grupo. Sus duelos épicos constituyen la mayor parte de esta película.

725768.title: Horse Boxing Killer
725768.description: A fighter and a martial arts warrior combine forces and practice the Art of Horse Boxing under the instruction of the Drunken Master Sam Seed.

100000278.title: Ordinary Man
100000278.description: Three friends embark on the road to Jiangnan to safely escort Princess Zhao Yuhuan, and during their journey, the group is faced with many obstacles.

100000964.title: The Fearless Three
100000964.description: A teenager has been tasked with keeping the legacy of her birth father alive by winning an annual martial arts tournament, given in his honor.

100001022.title: Force: Five
100001022.description: A martial arts expert leads a team of martial artists to rescue a senator's daughter from an island fortress ruled by the leader of a religious cult.

100001030.title: Revenge of the Ninja
100001030.description: When a band of assassins slaughters the family of Cho Osaki, he flees to America but soon discovers a ruthless drug trafficker intent on killing him.

100001555.title: Ten Fingers of Death
100001555.description: Having secretly learned Kung Fu from an old beggar from the woods, an underprivileged young man fights to protect his town from a crime syndicate.

100001663.title: The Vanished Jade Seal
100001663.description: When the imperial jade seal disappears, the palace is thrown into disarray as the prince hatches a plan and brothers turn against each other.

100002096.title: La Conexión Del Frasco De Jade (Doblado)
100002096.description: A medida que los gobiernos ruso y chino llegan a acuerdos de paz, los traidores de ambos lados intentan instigar una guerra entre los países.

100002112.title: Kill Bill: Vol. 1
100002112.description: After waking up from a four-year coma, a former assassin seeks revenge on the team of killers that betrayed her—and that she was once a part of.

100002159.title: Kill Bill: Vol. 2
100002159.description: The Bride continues her quest for revenge, fighting her way through a host of assassins in pursuit of a final showdown with the man who betrayed her.

100002621.title: Crazy Fist
100002621.description: Years after retiring, a former MMA champion has no choice but to step back in the ring when his best friend dies under suspicious circumstances.

100002628.title: Ip Man: The Awakening
100002628.description: While in Hong Kong, a young Master Ip intervenes in a kidnapping attempt, unintentionally igniting a turf war with a ruthless human trafficking ring.

100002657.title: The Unity of Heroes
100002657.description: A dangerous narcotic is about to be distributed across the country by a corrupt pharmaceutical company, and it’s up to Wong Fei Hung to stop it.

100002666.title: Shadow Master
100002666.description: After being slain by a group of criminals, a man is reborn with animal-like superpowers and makes it his mission to right the wrongs of his city.

100002707.title: Clash of Empires
100002707.description: In this epic adventure, a great warrior embraces his destiny when he finds himself in the middle of a grave conflict between three powerful empires.

100002797.title: Kung Fu Boys
100002797.description: A Chinese-American problem child with a superhero dream becomes involved in an international crime when he’s sent to Shenzhen to live with his uncle.

0300007891.title: Secret of the Sword
0300007891.description: A quest of high-flying martial arts action begins in order to find an ancient scroll that unlocks secrets of the sword and total Kung-Fu domination.
